   <conbody>
      <p class="- topic/p ">Press the<uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol "> Section</uicontrol> button to show detailed information about the
         measurement data of a section. You can quickly change to another section by pressing the
         Section <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">arrow </uicontrol>buttons.</p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">Press on a bottle image to show only that bottle and related information. Press again on the bottle image to show all bottles again.  Press on a bottle to see more data about a specific cavity.</p>
